Message.SourceString: Oh no, not another human. You gonna just leave me to die too? Like the last one did?
Message.LocalizedString: Oh no, not another human. You gonna just leave me to die too? Like the last one did?

Message.SourceString: Hrmm? How are you getting on? Got me any antlers yet?
Message.LocalizedString: Hrmm? How are you getting on? Got me any antlers yet?

Message.SourceString: I still ain't talkin' to no stinky human. Get lost!
Message.LocalizedString: I still ain't talkin' to no stinky human. Get lost!

Message.SourceString: Speaking of going places, you mention he's exploring a dragonkin vault in the swamps? I think you probably want to go and take a look. No?
Message.LocalizedString: Speaking of going places, you mention he's exploring a dragonkin vault in the swamps? I think you probably want to go and take a look. No?

Message.SourceString: Not got the ingredients yet? I need you to hunt a deer and bring me one of their antlers. Deers are flighty creatures, and easily spooked.
Message.LocalizedString: Not got the ingredients yet? I need you to hunt a deer and bring me one of their antlers. Deers are flighty creatures, and easily spooked.

Message.SourceString: Ah... the castle, not ideal. That place is a veritable goblin stronghold. Go see if you can find him, but make sure you're geared up for a fight.
Message.LocalizedString: Ah... the castle, not ideal. That place is a veritable goblin stronghold. Go see if you can find him, but make sure you're geared up for a fight.

Message.SourceString: But, if he's braving the garou, he must know a way of dealing with Velgar. There's no other reason he'd do something quite so stupid.
Message.LocalizedString: But, if he's braving the garou, he must know a way of dealing with Velgar. There's no other reason he'd do something quite so stupid.

Message.SourceString: So, young Cathan's pushing his way into Ghornfell, eh? Reckless, as always, that boy's gonna get himself killed.
Message.LocalizedString: So, young Cathan's pushing his way into Ghornfell, eh? Reckless, as always, that boy's gonna get himself killed.

Message.SourceString: Argh, leave me alone human.
Message.LocalizedString: Argh, leave me alone human.

Message.SourceString: I've got something to give you, but you've got your hands full. Go clear some space and then come back to me.
Message.LocalizedString: I've got something to give you, but you've got your hands full. Go clear some space and then come back to me.

Message.SourceString: Got us all riled up. Promised us power and glory. Said he knews how to get rid of the big scaly war king.
Message.LocalizedString: Got us all riled up. Promised us power and glory. Said he knews how to get rid of the big scaly war king.

Message.SourceString: Look, I hate to ask this, but I need you to go after him. You need to fight your way into Ghornfell and pick up his trail.
Message.LocalizedString: Look, I hate to ask this, but I need you to go after him. You need to fight your way into Ghornfell and pick up his trail.

Message.SourceString: Ghornfell's no joke though, that's where the garou live and if you thought goblins were trouble you're in for a shock.
Message.LocalizedString: Ghornfell's no joke though, that's where the garou live and if you thought goblins were trouble you're in for a shock.

Message.SourceString: Here, this'll help get you started.
Message.LocalizedString: Here, this'll help get you started.

Message.SourceString: You'll find it easier to hunt one if you craft yourself a bow of some kind. The deer themselves are all over Bramblemead, finding them shouldn't be a problem.
Message.LocalizedString: You'll find it easier to hunt one if you craft yourself a bow of some kind. The deer themselves are all over Bramblemead, finding them shouldn't be a problem.

Message.SourceString: Just hunt one down, and bring me the antlers. You can keep all the other useful materials, maybe use them to craft better gear? You're looking a bit shabby.
Message.LocalizedString: Just hunt one down, and bring me the antlers. You can keep all the other useful materials, maybe use them to craft better gear? You're looking a bit shabby.

Message.SourceString: You're really struggling with this, aren't you? I'll walk you through exactly what to do, but I can't be holding your hand all the time.
Message.LocalizedString: You're really struggling with this, aren't you? I'll walk you through exactly what to do, but I can't be holding your hand all the time.

Message.SourceString: Discover, learn and improve. That's going to need to be your mantra on Ashenfall if you're going to survive. So find new materials, discover new recipes and then make them.
Message.LocalizedString: Discover, learn and improve. That's going to need to be your mantra on Ashenfall if you're going to survive. So find new materials, discover new recipes and then make them.

Message.SourceString: To hunt deer you'll want a bow. Find some flax and some wood, this should be enough to help you build a spinning wheel. There you'll make thread and with that you can craft a bow.
Message.LocalizedString: To hunt deer you'll want a bow. Find some flax and some wood, this should be enough to help you build a spinning wheel. There you'll make thread and with that you can craft a bow.

Message.SourceString: Well he got what he wanted, some weird dragonkin stuff, then he said he were heading into Ghornfell and that I'd just slow us down. The others agreed, gits.
Message.LocalizedString: Well he got what he wanted, some weird dragonkin stuff, then he said he were heading into Ghornfell and that I'd just slow us down. The others agreed, gits.

Message.SourceString: Find feathers to make arrows, and then you're good to go. While you're at it, look for recipes that will let you make stronger gear. You're going to need it.
Message.LocalizedString: Find feathers to make arrows, and then you're good to go. While you're at it, look for recipes that will let you make stronger gear. You're going to need it.

Message.SourceString: It homes in on the spiritual residue of our subject, in this case young Cathan, using this old shoe of his as a spiritual connection. Vile, but useful. Just don't sniff it.
Message.LocalizedString: It homes in on the spiritual residue of our subject, in this case young Cathan, using this old shoe of his as a spiritual connection. Vile, but useful. Just don't sniff it.

Message.SourceString: We'll then just point the antler at the map, and it'll point straight to where we'll find him... or at least where he's been most the last couple of days.
Message.LocalizedString: We'll then just point the antler at the map, and it'll point straight to where we'll find him... or at least where he's been most the last couple of days.

Message.SourceString: Now then, we just need to spread the rune essence like so. Add a dash of this weird unguent stuff Zanik made from snails, and then...
Message.LocalizedString: Now then, we just need to spread the rune essence like so. Add a dash of this weird unguent stuff Zanik made from snails, and then...

Message.SourceString: So I bet you're just like him, so I aint gonna talk to yous no more. Yeah, that'll teach yas!
Message.LocalizedString: So I bet you're just like him, so I aint gonna talk to yous no more. Yeah, that'll teach yas!

Message.SourceString: Ah excellent, you've got one, we can begin. This ritual is a bit old school, proper druidic guff, but it's handy in a pinch.
Message.LocalizedString: Ah excellent, you've got one, we can begin. This ritual is a bit old school, proper druidic guff, but it's handy in a pinch.

Message.SourceString: Not found young Cathan yet? Last we heard he'd been captured by the goblins up at the Brynmoor Castle. I'll need you to storm in there and rescue him.
Message.LocalizedString: Not found young Cathan yet? Last we heard he'd been captured by the goblins up at the Brynmoor Castle. I'll need you to storm in there and rescue him.

Message.SourceString: Any sign of young Cathan? What -- he escaped, even managed to turn a few goblins to his cause? Interesting lad that, going to go places.
Message.LocalizedString: Any sign of young Cathan? What -- he escaped, even managed to turn a few goblins to his cause? Interesting lad that, going to go places.

Message.SourceString: Horrible creatures, the garou. Deadly beastmen with no concept of mercy. You'll need to make sure you're as prepared as you can be, before you risk facing them in battle.
Message.LocalizedString: Horrible creatures, the garou. Deadly beastmen with no concept of mercy. You'll need to make sure you're as prepared as you can be, before you risk facing them in battle.

Properties.TextName: Return to the Wise old man
